data.description: Welcome home!  This classic Windsor Hills home features 3 bedrooms and could be 4 with an office, depending on how you designed it.  It appears that two bedrooms were converted to one large bedroom. The home's two living areas are spacious and light and the cook-friendly kitchen is accessible to both.  With a half bath off the utility room, a bonus sunroom that looks to a beautiful backyard, and wonderful neighbors, there is so much to love about this home. Years of memories were made here and now it's time to create your own.
